'''Cseria''' was the title given to the leaders of [[Elom/Legends|Elom]] community groups analogous to the role of a village [[Mayor/Legends|mayor]]. The communities, which lived in burrows known as [[sevriinas]],<ref name="GG12">''[[Galaxy Guide 12: Aliens — Enemies and Allies]]''</ref> were also known as cseria.<ref name="DB">{{DB|species|eloms|Eloms}}</ref> The cseria met every year to resolve problems until the arrival of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].<ref name="GG12" />

